{"tid":1599280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳秋北：示威者侮辱國旗即侮辱自己","createTime":"2019-09-28T01:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:16:28.000Z","uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":258,"uniUserReply":133,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f44229fe4d19ffb685413df960bcf4c878b5c5","tid":1599280,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"下周二是中共建政70周年，針對近日在反修例示威中焚燒及塗污國旗的情況，守護香港大聯盟將在當日發起「全港市民國慶護旗義工隊」，組織逾萬名義工在全港各區參與守護國旗行動。聯盟召集人黃英豪表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">短時間內未能準備義工制服，但有義工建議戴紅色帽作識別</span>，他<span style=\"color: red;\">強調護旗隊不會挑起爭端</span>及不會以武力護旗，會勸喻違法者及報警處理。教育局局長楊潤雄昨發信呼籲學生尊重國旗，強調侮辱國旗是違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n守護香港大聯盟下午召開記者會，宣佈在中共建政70周年發起「全港市民國慶護旗義工隊」，配合特區政府共同守護國旗，聯盟設立多個WhatsApp帳號供市民報名成為護旗義工，保障國旗免受侮辱。<span style=\"color: red;\">聯盟預期義工隊明日起成立，保守估計最少一萬名市民參加</span>。<br />\n<br />\n黃英豪批評，<span style=\"color: red;\">毀壞國旗的行動不止觸犯《國旗或國徽條例》，亦挑戰一國兩制底線，衝擊國家權威，傷害14億中華兒女的感情</span>，強調不能容忍暴徒的惡行，呼籲熱愛祖國的市民參與護旗的隊伍。他們<span style=\"color: red;\">亦建議政府向高等法院申請臨禁制令，將政府建築物外的旗桿下方圓數十米劃為禁區，防止有人破壞國旗</span>，同時呼籲警方要對破壞國旗的行為嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港區全國人大代表、守護香港大聯盟副召集人吳秋北指，國旗是國家象徵，代表14億人民的感情，示威者侮辱國旗的行為「令全中國人感情，以致尊嚴受到傷害，甚至佢（示威者）自己都係侮辱自己」</span>，他又呼籲全港市民守護國旗：「人人都是護旗手」。他稱護旗隊若目睹損毀國旗的行為只會勸喻和報警，他又呼籲護旗隊義工遵守香港法例不能毆鬥，盡量避免衝突。"},{"pid":"122580e30b01668d7f14f755e058639e1267e570","tid":1599280,"uid":51271,"like":458,"dislike":0,"score":458,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCcYToF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCcYToF.png&h=bcde6a7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"deb2df35e882270ea3845091f5fc55a41c6312a9","tid":1599280,"uid":75877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"122580e30b01668d7f14f755e058639e1267e570","tid":1599280,"uid":51271,"like":458,"dislike":0,"score":458,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCcYToF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCcYToF.png&h=bcde6a7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7683012270ad6bcb9cf25272bd30fcc75492841","tid":1599280,"uid":258696,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:52:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人<br />\n林鄭一邊捉年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一邊假對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再自high 咩8黃2藍了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n杯葛對話會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />929 全球反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />101 慶佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"00f2ad353ef63bba37c4b164e1167bf970bdcfe0","tid":1599280,"uid":29917,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:52:48.000Z","msg":"身為國人，何其恥辱"},{"pid":"9b33428f174a488945c9e552c3fd2777c6f0a6d8","tid":1599280,"uid":23023,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"支那國旗不代表我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b5aae62b14d2e0ce6b71a80482e0b069e396f4","tid":1599280,"uid":39710,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"又代表14億人<img src=\"/asset