6g5yp3tllkxx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpadlet.com%2Flennonnewshk%2F6g5yp3tllkxx&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=6bd8d2d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://padlet.com/lennonnewshk/6g5yp3tllkxx</a><br />\nTG 訂閱 : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e76ff0d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"3c6c7192a58e09314ddcea4e38cc8589b2952690","tid":1599280,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:45:08.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家將呢支旗象徵運動嘅幟帶上街頭<br />\n我哋唔要紅旗五星洋紫荊！<br />\n<br />\n旗幟由攬炒標誌延伸而成<br />\n五個人字聚首一堂，象徵香港人五大訴求<br />\n構圖既似傘、又像一朵綻放的木棉花<br />\n<br />\n木棉係香港土生品種，秋冬落葉<br />\n捱過凜冽寒冬而後花開<br />\n初夏飛絮處處，猶如今年香港經歷六月霜<br />\n木棉樹幹壯碩而挺直，一樹傲骨，所以又稱「英雄樹」<br />\n<br />\n而且木棉生命力驚人，那怕是多惡劣的環境，都可以挣扎成長<br />\n加上耐旱耐風，恰似香港人性格頑強而擇善固執<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家將呢支旗幟帶上街頭<br />\n以表達香港運動，遍地開花的精神<br />\n<br />\nFile 歡迎自行download，隨便用～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUOpqfu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUOpqfu.jpg&h=8f5bf0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1:2<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1BT3vJWDHBF3H26IcyYtz-YDCAzDEIBuq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1BT3vJWDHBF3H26IcyYtz-YDCAzDEIBuq&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e7263ff0\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1BT3vJWDHBF3H26IcyYtz-YDCAzDEIBuq</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3QZYAy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3QZYAy.jpg&h=e54b77c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2:3<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1h-HWnwdabuv0_p3MlAOUsEG27JmmD3-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1h-HWnwdabuv0_p3MlAOUsEG27JmmD3-I&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=6e58d822\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1h-HWnwdabuv0_p3MlAOUsEG27JmmD3-I</a><br />\n<br />\nAI <br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1O7c3Jz3xo4_baPmfGORyEbLFYbTh2O2t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1O7c3Jz3xo4_baPmfGORyEbLFYbTh2O2t&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjzsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e0692b07\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1O7c3Jz3xo4_baPmfGORyEbLFYbTh2O2t</a><br />\n<br />\n祝願<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！"},{"pid":"92458724c39ca5da47d5882cc413ef64241965f6","tid":1599280,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"哈巴狗吳秋北 你生存已經係侮辱全人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d4624845e7e6eff042b80a7e5cb69fa0bf4213","tid":1599280,"uid":227303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"631d973cc7e4a1a2a3d64ef2dd626bab6c01dda6","tid":1599280,"uid":35804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"侮辱自己都要你管？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:46:00.000Z","msg":"笑L死"},{"pid":"62c020cffe7dd3089d58b650b30f8248118362aa","tid":1599280,"uid":291526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"如果我係外國籍呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c73859524073450bb5440800b54577ad149f71","tid":1599280,"uid":266741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6f44229fe4d19ffb685413df960bcf4c878b5c5","tid":1599280,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"下周二是中共建政70周年，針對近日在反修例示威中焚燒及塗污國旗的情況，守護香港大聯盟將在當日發起「全港市民國慶護旗義工隊」，組織逾萬名義工在全港各區參與守護國旗行動。聯盟召集人黃英豪表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">短時間內未能準備義工制服，但有義工建議戴紅色帽作識別</span>，他<span style=\"color: red;\">強調護旗隊不會挑起爭端</span>及不會以武力護旗，會勸喻違法者及報警處理。教育局局長楊潤雄昨發信呼籲學生尊重國旗，強調侮辱國旗是違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n守護香港大聯盟下午召開記者會，宣佈在中共建政70周年發起「全港市民國慶護旗義工隊」，配合特區政府共同守護國旗，聯盟設立多個WhatsApp帳號供市民報名成為護旗義工，保障國旗免受侮辱。<span style=\"color: red;\">聯盟預期義工隊明日起成立，保守估計最少一萬名市民參加</span>。<br />\n<br />\n黃英豪批評，<span style=\"color: red;\">毀壞國旗的行動不止觸犯《國旗或國徽條例》，亦挑戰一國兩制底線，衝擊國家權威，傷害14億中華兒女的感情</span>，強調不能容忍暴徒的惡行，呼籲熱愛祖國的市民參與護旗的隊伍。他們<span style=\"color: red;\">亦建議政府向高等法院申請臨禁制令，將政府建築物外的旗桿下方圓數十米劃為禁區，防止有人破壞國旗</span>，同時呼籲警方要對破壞國旗的行為嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港區全國人大代表、守護香港大聯盟副召集人吳秋北指，國旗是國家象徵，代表14億人民的感情，示威者侮辱國旗的行為「令全中國人感情，以致尊嚴受到傷害，甚至佢（示威者）自己都係侮辱自己」</span>，他又呼籲全港市民守護國旗：「人人都是護旗手」。他稱護旗隊若目睹損毀國旗的行為只會勸喻和報警，他又呼籲護旗隊義工遵守香港法例不能毆鬥，盡量避免衝突。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:47:22.000Z","msg":"悔辱國旗，後悔不侮辱國旗。"},{"pid":"fcd753e6ea1d513a15baedd59f3f618cad868237","tid":1599280,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"你憑乜嘢或國旗代表我？"},{"pid":"29017090cc5a93c3d1d22e3140710226cd24f7e1","tid":1599280,"uid":3378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:48:41.000Z","msg":"侮辱自己都唔得？<br />\n香港真係無哂自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ddec4fb078f046db78c2e638a7fe48393ca3ed","tid":1599280,"uid":141668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"冇問題喎，話明攬炒㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02594675ecd990f053b6e113c79f6f5a292ca15a","tid":1599280,"uid":59684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEqS3xy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEqS3xy.png&h=5d2e907f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80dc7fee70e81cef1f7f3fd8e29b6acfbc0ed8ec","tid":1599280,"uid":112622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"